adjustDecimals.tsol
├── when decimals are equal
│   └── it should return values unchanged
└── when decimals are not equal
    ├── when at least one decimal is greater than 18
    │   └── it should revert
    └── when both decimals are less than, or equal to, 18
        ├── when values overflow when adjusted
        │   └── it should revert
        └── when values can be adjusted without overflow
            └── it should return the adjusted values with base 18 decimals